489
00:58:27,250 --> 00:58:29,541
The boy lived here with that big fish.

490
00:58:29,708 --> 00:58:33,708
It made him think that it was his.

491
00:58:37,166 --> 00:58:38,125
And then one day,

492
00:58:40,500 --> 00:58:42,291
law enforcement like yourself

493
00:58:43,250 --> 00:58:47,416
brought this thing called justice.

494
00:58:55,125 --> 00:58:57,375
