495
00:58:58,166 --> 00:58:59,708
was no longer his.

496
00:59:08,000 --> 00:59:08,916
Remember me.

497
00:59:09,666 --> 00:59:12,666
My name is Alhawi Yalu.

498
00:59:25,000 --> 00:59:26,083
Alhawi Yalu.

499
00:59:27,000 --> 00:59:28,625
I understand why you did it.

500
00:59:28,791 --> 00:59:30,041
Kamnan Jun is crooked.

501
00:59:30,791 --> 00:59:33,458
That's why I sent you a message
that all of them were here.

502
00:59:35,500 --> 00:59:37,083
As long as I'm still alive,

503
00:59:38,333 --> 00:59:40,333
