to send new people here.

504
00:59:43,791 --> 00:59:44,833
We can work together

505
00:59:46,166 --> 00:59:47,666
to make this town a better place.

506
00:59:53,333 --> 00:59:56,541
Comfort and well-being
are only for the ruling class.

507
00:59:58,750 --> 01:00:01,208
What are you trying to do, master?

508
01:00:01,916 --> 01:00:05,166
Trying to uphold justice, master?

509
01:00:06,458 --> 01:00:08,916
I am the justice!

510
01:00:12,916 --> 01:00:16,291
What you do... is against the law.

511
01:00:18,625 --> 01:00:21,541
Between you and I,
the difference is the uniform.

512
01:00:25,000 --> 01:00:27,500
This place can exist without you!

513
01:01:11,416 --> 01:01:13,458
I don't think anyone will show up today.

514
01:01:14,333 --> 01:01:17,041
I suggest that we call it a day.

515
01:01:23,500 --> 01:01:24,375
Why?

516
01:01:26,875 --> 01:01:28,875
-They want to be outlaws so bad?
-Khun Pun!

517
01:01:29,291 --> 01:01:31,791
-Khun Pun! Bad news!
-What's going on?

518
01:01:34,375 --> 01:01:35,791
We just learned that

519
01:01:36,166 --> 01:01:40,416
Alhawi Yalu knows
that Khaitoh's village saved your life.

520
01:01:41,541 --> 01:01:43,208
They're heading there right now.

521
01:01:43,833 --> 01:01:46,416
What should we do, sir?

522
01:01:50,041 --> 01:01:52,083
-Is that true?
-Yes, sir.

523
01:01:53,625 --> 01:01:55,041
Hey!

524
01:02:13,875 --> 01:02:15,583
Hurry! Go to the village!

525
01:03:54,541 --> 01:03:57,541
Tell everyone in the village. From now on,

526
01:03:58,000 --> 01:04:00,208
they owe me their lives.

527
01:04:16,833 --> 01:04:17,791
Suea Sang,

528
01:04:18,416 --> 01:04:21,625
